{"tid":1486932,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《PRODUCE101》爆連續4季都造假！ 「關鍵錄音檔曝光」警申請2次搜查令","createTime":"2019-08-19T04:50:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T08:44:56.000Z","uid":74065,"like":36,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"0f4b29d5425aeadfa3fe7e1b0c69ee011e1db95b","tid":1486932,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:50:59.000Z","msg":"從韓節目《PRODUCE X 101》脫穎而出的11人組X1倒數8天出道，怎料19日卻爆出造假搜查案的新進度，不只這一季連前面3季也受到影響，警方12日向CJ E&amp;M辦公室和節目製作組居住地第二次申請了搜索令。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4314/4314400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4314%2F4314400.jpg&h=b8a39382&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲《PRODUCE X 101》爆作假證據被查到。（圖／翻攝自NATE）<br />\n<br />\n據韓媒《中央日報》報導，首爾警察廳網絡搜查隊7月31日申請了第一次搜查令後，扣查了CJ E&amp;M辦公室裡和文字投票等檔案的相關資料進行調查，而在其中一台製作組人員的手機內，發現了直接提到「造假」的錄音檔，而且不只這次引起爭議的第四季，也有提到其他幾季造假相關內容。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4314/4314421.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4314%2F4314421.jpg&h=5affbb9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲《PRODUCE 101》連續4季出道組結果都涉嫌造假。（圖／翻攝自I.O.I、WANNA ONE、IZ*ONE、X1推特）<br />\n<br />\n因此，警方8月12日第二次申請了CJ E&amp;M辦公室和節目製作組居住地的搜索令且展開扣押調查。據悉，警方正在考慮以妨礙業務罪名對《PRODUCE X 101》投票造假立案，而他們受訪時回應：「在調查進行中對外說明狀況恐被認定是發佈被懷疑事實，這不是警方能詳細幫確認每一條細項的內容。」<br />\n<br />\n新聞一出瞬間就衝上各大南韓搜尋引擎網站熱新聞，X1粉絲對此感到相當焦急，期望著不會影響到目前11人的出道未來，另一部分網友則認為「這樣還要讓他們（X1）出道嗎」、「IZ*ONE還在活動也會受到影響吧」、「放過這些追夢的孩子吧」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望牙降自首<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4897f2e0c4a540195e8dec6147635c293e07394a","tid":1486932,"uid":46435,"like":27,"dislike":15,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:54:26.000Z","msg":"牙降又係到累人累物 唉.."},{"pid":"d6feb581279b812a2e17556fa359617d71990620","tid":1486932,"uid":205928,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:54:46.000Z","msg":"我大爆射車汪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6773fd12eda73cf9d4bb4859d2fa01d091545d5b","tid":1486932,"uid":189235,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:55:46.000Z","msg":"查yg嗰幾個又唔見咁有心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec0773c062bfdfe1a325a65eb5c2ccafc4201c7","tid":1486932,"uid":238483,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:06:33.000Z","msg":"連續四季=包括I.O.I<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a5c205304258810cb0f7970c1d7618b335ddc79","tid":1486932,"uid":174744,"like":30,"dislike":7,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:09:43.000Z","msg":"Mnet同經理公司問題關練習生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪再黑采源啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97557b11ce9b4327eeed8ca11ad06f2b62ac4ea7","tid":1486932,"uid":292624,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:10:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f00c708f9e00cea8ce76b6a66daa156aeaa30183","tid":1486932,"uid":31540,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:26:49.000Z","msg":"Ioi假得幾真"},{"pid":"29c2927dba2265c4ab57c3ff56c078fc15a7b6f5","tid":1486932,"uid":4679,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:39:01.000Z","msg":"Ioi唔會造假掛 最多分多啲鏡頭比金素慧等推佢出道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c14c6fc571fa859826a80acaaee89790aea68a2","tid":1486932,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:39:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"626e92c9b09e6123b1ca2295e639310b4a954751","tid":1486932,"uid":229026,"like":33,"dislike":6,"score":27,